Sentencas: The composite cathode LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 (LBM-SDC) was prepared by glycine-nitrate combustion method.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The phase and morphology evolution of the composite cathode were characterized by X-ray diffraction (XRD) and scanning electron microscopy (SEM), respectively.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The results showed that LBM had good chemical stability with SDC at 1 000 degrees C. Due to the introduction of SDC, the length of the thriple-phase boundary was extended and the thermal matching between the cathode and the electrolyte was enhanced, resulting in an improvement in the electrochemical performance of the composite cathode.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The electrochemical impedance spectrum (EIS) results indicated that the cathode polarization resistance (1?,) decreased steadily with the addition of SDC.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The optimum addition of 30%(w/w) SDC in the composite cathode leads to the lowest R, of 0.186 Sicm(2) at 700 degrees C in air, which is 74% less than the pristine LBM cathode (Rp=0.717 SZ cm(2)).
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: This is because an additional oxygen ion conduction path is generated after the introduction of SDC; thereby the oxygen reduction reaction is promoted.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The maximum power density of the electrolyte-support single cell Ni-SDC/SDC/LBM-30% SDC reached 234 mWcm' at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The power density maintains a stable value at 230 mWcm' throughout a test period of 90 h, indicating that LBM-30%SDC had sufficient stability during the operation.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs

Sentencas: The oxygen partial pressure measurement indicated that the oxygen molecule adsorption-diffusion process is the reaction rate-limiting step of the composite cathode.
Titulo: Preparation and Electrochemical Properties of LaBiMn2O6-Sm0.2Ce0.8OL9 Composite Cathode for IT-SOFCs
